What is the Gospel<br /> Week 5: Battling Unbelief through Faith<br /> Week 6: The Purpose of Missions<br /> Week 7: Gospel Proclamation through Word and Deed<br /> <br /> *Class fee includes bound &amp; published participant guide.</p>]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"6055f16b-c2d8-4f28-bad2-9e121e3d1a82\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>","{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"160\"}");
INSERT INTO jos_zoo_item VALUES("11","9","class","Going Deeper in the Word","going-deeper-in-the-word","2011-08-02 15:10:31","2011-09-06 22:23:44","42","2011-08-02 15:10:31","0000-00-00 00:00:00","0","0","1","1","42","","1","<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<elements>\n<select identifier=\"23c51773-2821-4500-aff4-288d40077efd\">\n  <option><![CDATA[austin-high]]></option>\n</select>\n<link identifier=\"591309db-4d33-4c05-9583-df773e8552c8\">\n  <value><![CDATA[www.regonline.com/goingdeeperintheword]]></value>\n  <text/>\n  <target/>\n  <custom_title/>\n  <rel/>\n</link>\n<text identifier=\"8ec757c9-819f-4a86-a2c6-e541173009a1\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Su]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"bbcdf21d-538c-44a6-a610-ae0d44231faa\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Sep 25-Nov 20]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"a4dbc779-3d4e-4e9d-a6fa-4ae80cf537bf\">\n  <value><![CDATA[9:00-10:45am]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"601d851e-74e7-4483-88d1-645e168eab25\">\n  <value><![CDATA[9 weeks]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"89da3d28-8ad4-4e39-9291-9c6de3a3f7c9\">\n  <value><![CDATA[5+ hours of homework per week]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"8572e862-0093-4495-9015-1bb61ca27dfb\">\n  <value><![CDATA[$20]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"3a93ed1f-382b-4d84-98c0-5061af342d8b\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Fabienne Harford]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"3f4be974-e0c5-4256-887f-c4f3ffd353a6\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Women]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"acd8f0c9-89f2-4a1d-a946-6e604d886f8a\">\n  <value><![CDATA[<p>Have you ever wandered how you can hear from God? &nbsp;Are you eager to have two-way conversations with Him? Join us as we learn how to go deeper into the Word of God. &nbsp;God has called us to know Him. &nbsp;Growing in your ability to hear from Him through digging into His Word will transform your relationship with Him and your relationships with others. &nbsp;This is an intensive lab-style class, and it will require a considerable amount of time outside of class.</p>]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"6055f16b-c2d8-4f28-bad2-9e121e3d1a82\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>","{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"157\"}");
