ers and affects our everyday life.&nbsp; There is no pre-requisite for this class and it is the entry point for anyone that desires to serve within the Gospel Counseling ministry. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"6055f16b-c2d8-4f28-bad2-9e121e3d1a82\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>","{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"162\"}");
