f Jesus. You will participate in hands-on cross cultural experiences and will be assisted in identifying barriers and bridges to building relationships cross-culturally. <br /><br />This course requires the books <em>Crossing Cultures </em>and <em>Who is my Neighbor?</em>]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"6055f16b-c2d8-4f28-bad2-9e121e3d1a82\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>","{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"162\"}");
