INSERT INTO jos_zoo_search_index VALUES("17","acd8f0c9-89f2-4a1d-a946-6e604d886f8a","Spend time with others in this important life stage and learn principles of a Godly marriage, while discussing practical issues that we face when two become one. This class is meant to connect couples to a missional community, and participants will be required to participate in a mid-week missional community during the class (you\'ll be able to select a night(s) that work with your schedule when you sign up. If you\'re already in a missional community, we suggest temporarily leaving your existing group for this class. Please consider taking the class after you have completed Pre-Marital counseling. ONLY ONE PERSON FROM EACH COUPLE NEEDS TO REGISTER.  Week 1 - Intro/Get to know you Week 2 - Biblical Foundations of Marriage Week 3 - Needs/Roles/Responsibilities Week 4 - Conflict Resolution Week 5 - Communication Leading to Full Disclosure Week 6 - Finances and In Laws Week 7 - Sex and Sexuality Week 8 - Q&A Panel");
INSERT INTO jos_zoo_search_index VALUES("17","6055f16b-c2d8-4f28-bad2-9e121e3d1a82","\"1) The class encouraged my wife and me to engage in fruitful discussions, 2) The class provided a venue for making friends in the same life stage, who we now live missionally alongside, 3) The class informed us about marriage and how Scripture defines and guides this relationship.\"   \"This class has given us a great group of fellow believers and new friends to love and to be on mission with.  It has given us great understanding and wisdom to apply to our marriage to glorify God in it.\"   \"It has better prepared me for the reality of marriage.\"");
